l/202003/10/P2020031000361.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202003%2F10%2FP2020031000361.htm&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krK6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=5208580e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/10/P2020031000361.htm</a><br />\n房委會通過凍結出租租者置其屋計劃（租置計劃）屋邨的回收單位，以便日後出售這些單位。<br />\n行政長官於《2019年施政報告》建議房委會積極部署，加快出售39個租置屋邨中的未售單位。過去五年，房委會每年從租置屋邨自然回收約1 200個出租單位，以及每年平均出售約3 100單位予租置計劃現租戶。<br />\n  截至二○一九年十二月底，在184 000個可供出售的租置單位中，<span style=\"color: red;\">約有41 000個單位（即約22%）仍未售出。各租置屋邨的售出率各有不同，介乎約45%至93%之間。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/26/P2020022600376.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F26%2FP2020022600376.htm&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krK6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=1f884b29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/26/P2020022600376.htm</a><br />\n重推租置計劃會在短期內減少可供編配的公共租住房屋（公屋）單位數目，無可避免會延長公屋申請家庭的輪候時間。<span style=\"color: red;\">鑑於目前公屋供應嚴重不足，從有效運用房屋資源的角度來說，暫時難以推行。</span>"},{"pid":"cd3bb5b34aeb4afd4514f62ab70a31b48202a0af","tid":2025415,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>約有41 000個單位（即約22%）仍未售出。各租置屋邨的售出率各有不同，介乎約45%至93%之間。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/common/pdf/about-us/housing-authority/ha-paper-library/SHC05-20RTC.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcommon%2Fpdf%2Fabout-us%2Fhousing-authority%2Fha-paper-library%2FSHC05-20RTC.pdf&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krK6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=28e95ba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/common/pdf/about-us/housing-authority/ha-paper-library/SHC05-20RTC.pdf</a><br />\n未售單位數目 未售單位百份比 <br />\n富善 1670 30.3%<br />\n良景 2101 30.7%<br />\n長發 875 34.7%<br />\n翠屏北  2412 39.0%<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">山景  4772 55.2% </span>"},{"pid":